{"tid":1540301,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"下一步將有可能係扔隻狗去死","createTime":"2019-09-04T11:14:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T13:29:49.000Z","uid":40226,"like":161,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"703b3432a371793771adc2ccbf66b0feceb9d377","tid":1540301,"uid":40226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:14:11.000Z","msg":"首先林鄭行撤回呢一步<span style=\"color: red;\">最主要目的未必係令淺黃返屋企</span><br />\n我睇完佢呢個行動我係好撚嬲<br />\n嬲到仆街<br />\n<br />\n相信大家到今時今日最撚憎一定係班狗<br />\n但請大家仔細一諗<br />\n林鄭做<span style=\"color: red;\">呢一步一定唔係一時興起</span><br />\n大家睇返<span style=\"color: red;\">呢排發生嘅事</span><br />\n啲狗越黎越亂鳩咁黎<br />\n仲有之前<span style=\"color: red;\">所謂流出</span>嘅林鄭承諾警隊將唔會有獨立調查委員會<br />\n仲有831嘅故意隱瞞<br />\n全部嘢都話緊比我地知一樣嘢<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">班狗將唔會受到應有嘅懲罰</span><br />\n我認為依家係有一種請君入甕嘅感覺<br />\n佢<span style=\"color: red;\">將民憤激發到一個極點</span><br />\n仲要喺呢個時候<span style=\"color: red;\">走返大陸</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">留個張建宗喺到</span><br />\n究竟係想點？<br />\n我認為到時佢會<span style=\"color: red;\">要求狗喺近日嘅示威放軟手腳</span><br />\n營造一個<span style=\"color: red;\">狗係受害者嘅錯覺</span><br />\n必要時<span style=\"color: red;\">派一條友去死</span><br />\n而呢條友亦唔需要係真狗<br />\n可以搵人扮<br />\n<br />\n到時將會<span style=\"color: red;\">扭轉成個國際輿論</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">美國推人權法案可能會受挫</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地最大嘅一張牌將會被無效化</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我認為喺目前呢個<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武行動嚴重受挫嘅局勢</span><br />\n我地需要<span style=\"color: red;\">暫時先重回和理非</span><br />\n黎一次<span style=\"color: red;\">大遊行</span><br />\n企出黎<span style=\"color: red;\">話畀國際聽我地唔撚收貨</span>呀屌你老母<br />\n班黑警有乜理由唔需要受懲罰？<br />\n咁撚樣嘅制度下<br />\n同直接送我地中係冇分別！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">待美國國會再開<br />\n人權法案塵埃落定<br />\n再考慮下一步行動</span><br />\n<br />\n當然<span style=\"color: red;\">我嘅諗法仍有不足</span><br />\n我好希望大家一齊brainstorm諗下點拆"},{"pid":"0d9f2d8f5a52827c58b0781a178cb00d447bde20","tid":1540301,"uid":40226,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:15:52.000Z","msg":"若果可以希望大家用其他途俓將我呢篇文share去facebook<br />\n甚至係其他政治人物到<br />\n畀更多人睇到"},{"pid":"b69545ea570c2ed87d1c575aaa97fedd6b804c0a","tid":1540301,"uid":40226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:16:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a58bc6defed56b5e3e352246e09091ffe27fed0e","tid":1540301,"uid":40226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:16:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d9a4ff3b630753f3f0c31fc8493fa656213382c","tid":1540301,"uid":40226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:16:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfdc551cbd3aaa2e1bf3a1213365be367053f4dd","tid":1540301,"uid":40226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:16:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f824f27f6766fa2f03568d52c3c0c1ce18a9794","tid":1540301,"uid":40226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:16:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8812205f1476bc4bc9e67a387e2ee55d53617da2","tid":1540301,"uid":40226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:16:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07bac2766d48ca5fb79f3524b501f2d1c950bfbe","tid":1540301,"uid":40226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:17:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d5aab6a6e04e3f107bd789d2d61730b6b2fd9e","tid":1540301,"uid":141871,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:17:40.000Z","msg":"其實你有啲紅字都唔係重點黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c33f502657e1afe668a