-size: xx-large;\">時代革命</span></strong></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">流水革命</span></strong></div>"},{"pid":"29a80fa16917be2e5985420f239c684096ae1584","tid":1540301,"uid":40226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:27:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdb28cbfcca48530d3fbf615b45af7f1deea972c","tid":1540301,"uid":40226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:27:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d7de588f6c333a1942f4aa54dfac8abb4bbcb0c","tid":1540301,"uid":40226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:27:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4265c4846325b647ddaf570dd51a35682cb0d460","tid":1540301,"uid":40226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:27:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67a3e4fcab11b7570fe9c02caebc2584d2a93073","tid":1540301,"uid":212336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:28:17.000Z","msg":"又一隻狗都唔死,屌你老母啦"},{"pid":"3fc66c9e2baeaf8f43052838d1f84a370dc33c7e","tid":1540301,"uid":40226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:28:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85cc6180fab43226700b4636b45f925a03a185c3","tid":1540301,"uid":53988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:28:40.000Z","msg":"死一隻狗&gt; who fucking cares<br />\n黑警死全家&gt;有啲睇頭<br />\n清算警隊&gt;咁先係做野架麻"},{"pid":"553ffb1cb68f6c5c47e9326acc2b4e1154f2179f","tid":1540301,"uid":40226,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"67a3e4fcab11b7570fe9c02caebc2584d2a93073","tid":1540301,"uid":212336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T1